Build Tower
https://www.codewars.com/kata/576757b1df89ecf5bd00073b

Build Tower by the following given argument:
number of floors (integer and always greater than 0).

Tower block is represented as *

Test cases
1	->		"*"
2	->		" * "
			"***"
3	->		"  *  "
			" *** "
			"*****"
			